query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS mlFixedFeeRanges (
  id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  minPrice DECIMAL(10,2) NOT NULL,
  maxPrice DECIMAL(10,2) NOT NULL,
  fixedFee DECIMAL(10,2) NOT NULL,
  description TEXT,
  createdAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL
);

INSERT INTO mlFixedFeeRanges (minPrice, maxPrice, fixedFee, description) VALUES
(0.00, 79.00, 6.00, 'Produtos até R$ 79 - Taxa fixa de R$ 6'),
(79.01, 999999.99, 0.00, 'Produtos acima de R$ 79 - Sem taxa fixa');
